{
  "stem": "4710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeshiva is a traditional way of learning boys Talmud.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite a hard regime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to get up very early and had to study till the evenings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Friday afternoon and Saturday was a bit easier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the rest of the week is quite hard learning, though I tried to make-- to mix it with a little bit of playing up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But otherwise, it-- you had to take it seriously.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because after end of the week, you had to-- there was a revision and you had to know what we have learned.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well what-- what I really liked to do, which I'm doing now, I like to-- I like always to pick on on people and teasing them, and especially when I was a youngster.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was [INAUDIBLE] making fun of everybody under the-- from our seniors as well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember that was-- even now I've got that feeling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes when there is-- when there is a comical situation, somebody looks ridiculous, I cannot help myself not to make fun of him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes it puts me quite an embarrassing position, when the other one doesn't see the joke of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I did that all the time in the Yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was just one year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because then it started in 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Normally, I think, looking at my older brothers, their situation, they learned from that age up to about 18, until they start taking some jobs or getting married-- almost to adulthood.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My younger brother was still at school at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't think it was-- it was all great difference.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, still we had the same shabbat meals.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
